<br>Ppt on methodological process and main results:  <a href="http://www.statistiques.public.lu/en/actors/statec/organisation/red/ecosol102015/StatisticsPortugal.pdf">http://www.statistiques.public.lu/en/actors/statec/organisation/red/ecosol102015/StatisticsPortugal.pdf</a> </p><p class="desc"><b>Database keywords:</b><br>Free or open access  ; Downloadable as excel files<br>Public institution<br>Institutional and quantitative (statistical) data ; Data on civic engagement, volunteering or participation</p><p class="keywords tohide">Portugal Portuguese ; English Free or open access  ; Downloadable as excel files NA NGOs/ Civil society</p></div></div></div></div>
<!-- item Portugal17 --><div class="list-item box"><div class="block"><p class="title">Voluntariado em Portugal: Contexto, Actores e Práticas (Volunteering in Portugal: Context, Actors and Practice)</p><p class="owner">Eugénio de Almeida Foundation, Private Institution for Social Solidarity</p><div data-collapse><div class="moreinfo">More info</div><div><p class="desc"><b>Data owner info:</b><br>Volunteering bank: bancodevoluntariado@fea.pt</p><P class="desc"><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i> The report presents an overview about volunteering in Portugal in the year of 2012. It includes the state of the art of the research on the topic, the numbers and facts, the legal framework, the organizational framework, management and practice, as well as the vision and challenges for the future.</p><p class="datalink"><i class="fa fa-laptop"></i> <b>Database:</b><br><a href="http://www.fundacaoeugeniodealmeida.pt/banco-voluntariado/?lang=pt">http://www.fundacaoeugeniodealmeida.pt/banco-voluntariado/?lang=pt</a>
<br>Knowledge Center:  <a href="http://www.fundacaoeugeniodealmeida.pt/banco-voluntariado/centro-de-conhecimento/2447.htm">http://www.fundacaoeugeniodealmeida.pt/banco-voluntariado/centro-de-conhecimento/2447.htm</a>
